bilingual.source: If you are not strapped in you would float around.

bilingual.source: Firstly, they had to float through a narrow 80-centimetre wide tube.

bilingual.source: The ball is hollow and can float on water.

bilingual.source: The hydrostatic principle explains why objects float or sink.

bilingual.source: The feather began to float down gently.

bilingual.source: Fishermen use a float to mark their nets.

list.abstract: FLOAT即单精度浮点型数据类型，数据类型用于存储单精度浮点数或双精度浮点数。 FLOAT具有4个字节，包括一个符号位、一个8位excess-127二进制指数和一个23位尾数，尾数表示一个介于1.0和2.0之间的数。由于尾数的高顺序位始终为1，因此它不是以数字形式存储的。
FLOAT是来自香港的潮流服饰品牌，始创于2008年，中文命名为“浮露”。专注于设计高机动性能的潮流服饰，并融合运动、团队精神、街头文化、现实批判主义等元素，以其别树一帜的简约多变风格著称。LOGO是一朵翻舌头的英雄花，象征“敢于向传统挑战的英雄”。

yingyinNormal.en: But it's not like you're going to float off the planet if you get too close to the Antarctic Peninsula, though you might weigh slightly less.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这不表示一靠近南极，你就会地从表浮起来 但你的体重会稍稍下降。

yingyinNormal.en: Here is Rebecca Rabbit with her little brother, Richard Rabbit. Hello, Rebecca. Hello, everyone. Richard, hold onto this float and you can practice kicking your legs.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是小兔瑞贝卡和她的弟弟，小兔理查德。你好，瑞贝卡！你们好啊！理查德抓住这块浮板然后练习用脚踢水。

yingyinNormal.en: The last time someone was allowed to be on a float was in the year 2000, a certain Jackie Chan.
yingyinNormal.zh: 上一次有人被允许乘上彩车还是在2000年，那就是成龙。

yingyinNormal.en: Ellie, it's so beautiful. We made it. We made it. Russell, we can float right over there. Climb up, climb up.
yingyinNormal.zh: Ellie，太美了，我们成功了，我们成功了， Russell ，我们可以飘过去，爬上去，爬上去。

yingyinNormal.en: I refuse to sink to his level. You can't sink. With all that helium in you, you're lucky you don't float away.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我才不要堕落到他那种水准。你落不了，体内充满了氦气，遇水不飘走就算你走运啦。

yingyinNormal.en: Sir, I don't float stories to see if they're seaworthy, and I don't give a shit about circulation. The only thing I care about is the truth.
yingyinNormal.zh: 先生，我绝不会捏造故事试探风向，我对发行量更是毫不在乎，我现在只关注真相。

yingyinNormal.en: Let's just call this what it is: blatant sensationalism, tied to the election, I don't float. Tied to an election to boost your circulation because the Herald is losing readership.
yingyinNormal.zh: 让我戳穿你的真实意图吧，你就是想趁大选搞个大新闻哗众取宠。我没有捏造...哗众取宠来提升你们的发行量，因为《先驱报》的读者在大量流失。

yingyinNormal.en: I am not going to be a spectator this evening, I am actually going to be part of the parade itself and I have the privilege of riding the Hong Kong Tourism Board Float and here she is.
yingyinNormal.zh: 今晚我不只是观众，事实上我本人也是游行的一份子，而且我还荣获特许能搭乘上香港旅游局的彩车，就是这辆。

yingyinNormal.en: So, I don't really have a job title or even a set place to work, so I kind of just float around and make sure everyone has what they need. 4:00, Your Honor. Don't forget to take your medicine.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的工作没有职称，也没有固定的工作地点，所以我就转来转去。确保所有人得到了需要的东西。四点了，法官大人，别忘了吃药。
